      p
        | And define your learning strengths and learning challenges using
        br
        a(href= "https://learningfromexperience.com/research-library/the-kolb-learning-style-inventory-4-0/" target="_blank")
          | The Kolb Learning Style Inventory 4.0
    .main__button
      a(href= "/app/en/instructions").button.button--secondary See Instructions


